###  https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Subsite_contains_a_Platform
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Subsite_contains_a_Platform> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                                                  rdfs:domain <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Subsite> ;
                                                                  rdfs:range <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Platform> ;
                                                                  rdfs:comment "A subsite contains one or more platforms."@en ,
                                                                               "Et underområde inneholder én eller flere plattformer."@no ,
                                                                               "Um subsítio contém uma ou mais plataformas."@pt ,
