###  https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#isERICMembershipOf
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#isERICMembershipOf> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                                         rdfs:domain <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#ERICMembership> ;
                                                         rdfs:range <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#RegionalFacility> ;
                                                         rdfs:comment "Collega un'entità di adesione ERIC alla infrastruttura regionale corrispondente."@it ,
