###  https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FAIRAssessmentTool
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FAIRAssessmentTool> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                         rdfs:subClassOf <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#SemanticTool> ;
                                                         rdfs:label "FAIR assessment tool"@en ,
                                                                    "FAIR-evalueringsverktøy"@no ,
                                                                    "Ferramenta de avaliação FAIR"@pt ,
                                                                    "Herramienta de evaluación FAIR"@es ,
                                                                    "Instrument de evaluare FAIR"@ro ,
                                                                    "Outil d'évaluation FAIR"@fr ,
                                                                    "Strumento di valutazione FAIR"@it ,
                                                                    "Εργαλείο αξιολόγησης FAIR"@el ;
                                                         <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A software tool used to assess the FAIRness of semantic artefacts."@en ,
                                                                                                          "Et programvareverktøy som brukes til å evaluere FAIR-nivået til semantiske artefakter."@no ,
                                                                                                          "Uma ferramenta de software utilizada para avaliar o nível de conformidade FAIR de artefactos semânticos."@pt ,
                                                                                                          "Un instrument software utilizat pentru evaluarea nivelului de conformitate FAIR al artefactelor semantice."@ro ,
                                                                                                          "Un outil logiciel utilisé pour évaluer le niveau de conformité FAIR d'artefacts sémantiques."@fr ,
                                                                                                          "Una herramienta de software utilizada para evaluar el grado de conformidad FAIR de artefactos semánticos."@es ,
                                                                                                          "Uno strumento software utilizzato per valutare il livello di conformità FAIR degli artefatti semantici."@it ,
                                                                                                          "Ένα εργαλείο λογισμικού που χρησιμοποιείται για την αξιολόγηση του επιπέδου FAIR σημασιολογικών τεχνουργημάτων."@el .


###  https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject
<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject> rdf:type owl:Class ;
